  "detailed_description": "Glowie Rammer<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><strong>Dynamic Driving Experience:</strong> Navigate through a changing landscape. Ram over glowies that spawn across the terrain to boost your speed and to earn points for each glowie taken down. <br><br><strong>Progressive Difficulty:</strong> The game ramps up in intensity the further you go, with faster and MORE glowies trying to hinder your ability to drive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115340/extras/cc792e704dbd82e67d4686431788bf52.poster.avif?t=1726715416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115340/extras/cc792e704dbd82e67d4686431788bf52.webm?t=1726715416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115340/extras/cc792e704dbd82e67d4686431788bf52.mp4?t=1726715416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>The bar indicates your movement. If your movement is too slow the glowies are able to get you so watch out!</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115340/extras/5be239cdcc0ad70ae30ee91e8c85473c.poster.avif?t=1726715416\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115340/extras/5be239cdcc0ad70ae30ee91e8c85473c.webm?t=1726715416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115340/extras/5be239cdcc0ad70ae30ee91e8c85473c.mp4?t=1726715416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
